==Honours==
* 1921 Conrad Brunner received the Marcel Benoist Prize in recognition of his achievements in the field of wound care and wound disinfection.<ref name="Benoist-Prize" />
* 1922 Conrad Brunner received an honorary philosophy doctorate from the University of Zurich for his research on the history of medicine.<ref name="HLS" />

